  <lyrics>[V1]
 Jan qhiti tumpirinich
 Samakascta.
 :Jesucristjarn janiw utjquit
 Qhuyapayir, munasiri.
 Jutamay Dios a j jar uñfiri. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Janiw yakha sutejj
 Churatáctanti.
 :Jesusaquiw khespiyiri
 Take juchanacasata
 Janc'aquiy cheka Diosar jutam. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Diosajj uruy arumaw
 Thakasctamjja.
 : Machak jacañ churanatac,
 Alajjpachan jacañatac
 ücanjj wiñayaw cusís jjáta. (Bis)
 
